b'{"data_headers":{"result_code":1},"data":{"information":{"article_id":1115,"category_name":"News","pr_category_id":"1","title_name":"Adding the Mana Spiral to More Adventurers!","message":"<div>In the notification titled &quot;Regarding Adjustments to Adventurers With Mana Spirals&quot; that was posted last month, director Yuji Okada announced that we would be unlocking the mana spiral for 3\\u2605 and 4\\u2605 shadow-attuned adventurers in February, but it is taking some additional time to make those adjustments.<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>Because of this, unlocking the mana spiral for 3\\u2605 shadow-attuned adventurers will be postponed until the end of March.<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>Thank you for your patience.<\/div><hr><div><br><\/div><div>A sixth mana circle, the mana spiral, will be added to certain adventurers starting <span class=\\"local_date\\" data-local_date=\\"1582869600\\"><\/span>.<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>The adventurers affected this time and their stats are described below.<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>\\u25a0Affected Adventurers<\/div><div>5\\u2605 Xainfried (Water\/lance)<\/div><div>5\\u2605 Nefaria (Shadow\/bow)<\/div><div>4\\u2605 Cleo (Shadow\/staff)<\/div><div><br><\/div><div><br><\/div><div>\\u25a0Stats<\/div><div>\\u30fb5\\u2605 adventurer<\/div><div>\\n<div class=\\"summonPickUp adjust\\">\\n<div class=\\"thumbList\\">\\n\\t<div class=\\"thumbnail\\">\\n\\t\\t<img src=\\"https:\/\/dragalialost.akamaized.net\/attached\/information\/images\/0a5c52e05ceea7549f1c619b029c14422.png\\">\\n\\t\\t<img class=\\"rarity\\" src=\\"https:\/\/dragalialost.akamaized.net\/attached\/information\/images\/23b8fc2cd656aa0d5ef96984f257ce7e2.png\\">\\n\\t<\/div>\\n\\t<div class=\\"discription\\">\\n\\t\\t<div class=\\"charaName\\">Xainfried<\/div><\/div>\\n<\/div>\\n\\n\\t<div class=\\"status\\">\\n\\t\\t<div class=\\"title\\">Stats<\/div>\\n\\t\\t<div class=\\"param\\">\\n\\t\\t\\t<div class=\\"base\\">\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<ul>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<li class=\\"lv