conds.<\/div><\/dd><dt><span><img src=\\"https:\/\/dragalialost.akamaized.net\/attached\/information\/images\/dffb0cc210e6ca60f7b0ec47d24543562.png\\"><\/span><span>HP 70% = Defense +15%<\/span><\/dt><dd><div>Increases defense by 15% when HP is 70% or above.<\/div><\/dd><\/dl><\/div><\/div><\/div><div><br><\/div><div>Notes:<\/div><div>1. The stats shown here represent the adventurer at level 100 with 70 mana nodes unbound.<\/div><div>2. The stats shown here do not include increases or decreases due to abilities.<\/div><div>3. The stats for the adventurer included in this notification shown in any prior notifications or preview videos were the stats at level 80 with 50 mana nodes unbound.<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>Thank you for playing Dragalia Lost.<\/div>","start_time":1582783200,"prev_article_id":"1114","next_article_id":"1108","image_path":"","update_time":1582788428}}}'